sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor Admin
  participant SP as SharePoint <br> Knowledge Base
  participant PA as Power Automate
  actor DO as Data Owner

  Admin->>SP: Set up Knowledge Base site <br> (library + key metadata)
  Admin->>PA: Configure automated workflows <br> (change trigger + scheduled review)

  PA->>SP: Monitor content updates <br> and review dates
  PA-->>DO: Send reminders <br> when review is required

  DO->>SP: Update content
  SP-->>PA: Trigger workflow
  PA-->>DO: Confirm review status updated